      "result": "{\"meta\": null, \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"{\\\"id\\\":3990262776,\\\"number\\\":28,\\\"state\\\":\\\"open\\\",\\\"locked\\\":false,\\\"title\\\":\\\"Release v1.1.0 - Bug fixes and utility additions\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"## Release v1.1.0\\\\n\\\\nThis release preparation PR integrates the critical fixes and utility additions needed for the v1.1.0 release cycle.\\\\n\\\\n### Integrated changes\\\\n\\\\n#### MetaSep token fix from PR #25\\\\n- Corrects `FormattingToken::MetaSep` so it maps to `\\\\u003c|meta_sep|\\\\u003e` instead of `\\\\u003c|channel|\\\\u003e`.\\\\n- Registers the missing `MetaSep` and `MetaEnd` formatting tokens in `src/registry.rs` for both native and WASM registry paths.\\\\n- Improves tokenizer registry behavior for meta formatting tokens.\\\\n\\\\n#### shadcn demo utility fix from PR #26\\\\n- Adds the missing `demo/harmony-demo/src/lib/utils.ts` helper with the `cn()` utility using `clsx` and `tailwind-merge`.\\\\n- Updates `.gitignore` to explicitly preserve `demo/harmony-demo/src/lib` so the shadcn utility file is not ignored.\\\\n\\\\n#### Release metadata\\\\n- Updates the Cargo package version to `1.1.0`.\\\\n- Adds a comprehensive `CHANGELOG.md` for v1.1.0 with added, fixed, changed, and technical details sections.\\\\n\\\\n### Commit structure\\\\nThe release branch intentionally contains four distinct release-preparation commits before merge:\\\\n1. MetaSep token fix\\\\n2. Utility file addition\\\\n3. Version update\\\\n4. Changelog addition\\\\n\\\\n### Pull request analysis performed\\\\nReviewed the current open PRs and selected the critical release-impacting changes from PR #25 and PR #26. Other open PRs were noted but not integrated into this focused release branch because they cover documentation formatting, README formatting, CI architecture expansion, and larger offline-tokenizer/race-condition API changes outside the requested release scope.\\\",\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T10:34:20Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T10:34:20Z\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"id\\\":191002565,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"U_kgDOC2J3xQ\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/191002565?v=4\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"gravatar_id\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"User\\\",\\\"site_admin\\\":false,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/events{/privacy}\\\",\\\"following_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/following{/other_user}\\\",\\\"followers_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/followers\\\",\\\"gists_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/gists{/gist_id}\\\",\\\"organizations_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/orgs\\\",\\\"received_events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/received_events\\\",\\\"repos_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/repos\\\",\\\"starred_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/starred{/owner}{/repo}\\\",\\\"subscriptions_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/subscriptions\\\"},\\\"draft\\\":false,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/harmony/pulls/28\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/harmony/pull/28\\\",\\\"issue_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/harmony/issues/28\\\",\\\"statuses_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/harmony/statuses/4d7dfed5eca119b0eaba7c51099ce91805936966\\\",\\\"diff_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/harmony/pull/28.diff\\\",\\\"patch_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/harmony/pull/28.patch\\\",\\\"commits_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/harmony/pulls/28/commits\\\",\\\"comments_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/harmony/issu